text: Elsie Kate Fisher (born April 3, 2003) is an American actress. She is best known for her starring role in the comedy-drama movie Eighth Grade (2018), for which she earned a nomination for the Golden Globe Award for Best Actress â€“ Motion Picture Comedy or Musical.
